@Node Overview "Overview"

	HTMLcat allows you to index your images into HTML pages.

@EndNode Overview

@Node instal

	Creates a copy of your catalogs into
	Local:catalogs/<language>

	Creates a copy of an Arexx script into Rexx

	Copies the program HTMLCAT lŕ oů where you want.

	In Extras you'll find few examples of images for your browser
		(gif format)


@EndNode instal


