@Node hist

	HTMLCAT V0.8 (17/02/97)

		First operationnal release.
		Shell mode only
		Only a few settings available


	HTMLCAT V1.2 (02/03/97)

		Graphical user interface (GUI)
		More settings available
		A new Arexx script (more user-frienly)

	HTMLCAT V2.01	(21/04/97)

		New GUI using "tabs"


	HTMLCAT V2.02	(15/05/97)

		Even more settings.
		Use local.
		now, you may save your settings (tooltypes)		

	HTMLCAT V2.03 (01/06/97)

		New option: uses HTML flags "width" and "height" in order
				to display thumbnails.
		Arexx script for GfxCon

	HTMLCAT V2.04 (10/06/97)
		Debug : Test height of window title bar for GUI
		Now Only create HTML 'link' for Gif, JPG, PNG pictures

	HTMLCAT V2.05 (16/06/97)
		Debug : Dest dir was not tested when creating Thumbnails. 



@EndNode hist


